Package: phyloPal
Type: Package
Title: Taxonomic Color Palettes and Alluvial-Dendrogram Visualization for Microbiome Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Magdalena W.", "Slawinska",
                  email = "mslawinska@mpipz.mpg.de",
                  role = c("aut", "cre"),
                  comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-6938-0270"))
Description: Tools for creating publication-ready microbiome visualizations. 
    Provides perceptually uniform HCL color palettes with 
    optional hierarchical grouping by higher taxonomy, taxonomic barplots, 
    alluvial plots for visualizing compositional changes across groups, and 
    combined alluvial-dendrogram layouts.
URL: https://github.com/mwslawinska/phyloPal, https://mwslawinska.github.io/phyloPal
BugReports: https://github.com/mwslawinska/phyloPal/issues
